    <measure>Alzheimer Disease Assessment Scale-Cognitive (ADAS-Cog)</measure>
    <time_frame>Tl. of 5 times: Once between Days 1-2, Once anytime between Days 3-14, Once anytime between Days 36-42, Once anytime between Days 64-70, Once between Days 92-97</time_frame>
  </secondary_outcome>
